<br>
i can summon a ring that has the same effect as dain cloak (spell haste 3), and my second ring was just the shadel bandit ring (not a uber ring that i would wear permanently).<br>
<br>
i received elemental barrier, so if i needed the extra fr/cr when solo or in a group setting, i will just use elemental barrier.<br>
<br>
being someone who likes hit points a great deal, i enjoy the extra 85 hp or so that the heiro cloak brings.<br>
<br>
if i need to put on resist gear, i have it.  if i need resist gear buffs, i have access to them.  if i need more resist gear, i stand by a bard while s/he sings their fr/cr resist song.  that (to me) makes up for the loss of fr/cr on dain's cloak, while putting me at a higher hp total which is good for all situations.<br>
